WEBVTT

00:01:01.490 --> 00:01:04.452
BOKER TOV.

00:01:04.452 --> 00:01:06.527
BOKER UNK

00:01:06.527 --> 00:01:10.545
TATSIGI ET ATSMEKH BEVAKASHA. MA SHMEKH?

00:01:10.545 --> 00:01:12.998
Leye Amdurski.

00:01:12.998 --> 00:01:14.244
ME-HABAYIT?

00:01:14.244 --> 00:01:16.281
Gertner.

00:01:16.281 --> 00:01:17.961
EFO NOLADET?

00:01:17.961 --> 00:01:23.583
NOLADTI BEKRUKI, LITOVSKI RESPUBLIKI.

00:01:23.583 --> 00:01:26.413
vifl kinder zent ir geven in shtub?

00:01:26.413 --> 00:01:30.810
zeks kinder: dray shvester un dray brider.

00:01:30.810 --> 00:01:34.262
zog nokh a mol, in velkhn yor bist du geboyrn?

00:01:34.262 --> 00:01:37.809
ikh bin geborn gevorn in a kleyne shtetele

00:01:37.809 --> 00:01:40.677
Kruki, Lite.

00:01:40.677 --> 00:01:42.488
in velkhn yor?

00:01:42.488 --> 00:01:44.884
in zibetstn yor.

00:01:44.884 --> 00:01:48.122
 in shtub zenen geven zeks kinder, yo?

00:01:47.941 --> 00:01:51.903
zeks kinder: dray brider un dray shvester zaynen mir geven.

00:01:51.903 --> 00:01:54.847
ye. zog, zog di nemen fun di kinder.

00:01:54.847 --> 00:01:58.603
mayn bruder, der eltster, hot geheysn Moyshe.

00:01:58.603 --> 00:02:01.848
der tsveyter bruder hot geheysn Berl.

00:02:01.848 --> 00:02:04.942
di shvester hot geheysn Nekhame.

00:02:04.942 --> 00:02:07.886
nokh a shvester hot geheysn Leye.

00:02:07.886 --> 00:02:10.961
a bruder hot geheysn Yosef.

00:02:10.961 --> 00:02:13.810
oy, kh'hob, Nekhame

00:02:13.810 --> 00:02:16.754
un Khaye; kh'hob a toes gehat.

00:02:16.754 --> 00:02:19.244
SLI- azoy.

00:02:19.244 --> 00:02:21.503
ikh ken nokh a mol iberzogn

00:02:21.150 --> 00:02:22.263
BEVAKASHA.

00:02:22.263 --> 00:02:25.413
der eltster bruder hot geheysn Moyshe.

00:02:25.413 --> 00:02:28.413
der tsveyter bruder hot geheysn Berl.

00:02:28.413 --> 00:02:31.243
di shvester hot geheysn Nekhame.

00:02:31.243 --> 00:02:34.225
nokh a shvester hot geheysn Khaye

00:02:34.225 --> 00:02:38.451
un a bruder Yosef, un ikh Leye.

00:02:38.451 --> 00:02:40.503
du bist geven di klenste in shtub?

00:02:40.319 --> 00:02:41.772
ye.

00:02:41.772 --> 00:02:46.281
ale brider mit, mit di shvester zenen geven shoyn, geheyrat?

00:02:46.281 --> 00:02:50.886
ah di shvester iz geven a geheyrate, un beyde brider di eltere.

00:02:50.886 --> 00:02:53.169
un zey hobn gehat kinder oykh?

00:02:53.169 --> 00:02:55.848
der tsveyter, Berl, hot gehat a zun.

00:02:55.848 --> 00:02:58.018
un di shvester Nekhame hot gehat

00:02:58.018 --> 00:03:01.905
i a zun un i a meydele.

00:03:01.905 --> 00:03:05.018
vi, vi hobn geheysn di eltern?

00:03:05.018 --> 00:03:07.735
der tate hot geheysn Motl

00:03:07.735 --> 00:03:10.394
un di mame hot geheysn SARA.

00:03:10.394 --> 00:03:14.753
un fun, fun di heym, vi hot zi geheysn?

00:03:14.753 --> 00:03:15.885
der tate?

00:03:15.885 --> 00:03:18.508
neyn, di, di mame fun di heym.

00:03:18.508 --> 00:03:22.508
di mame? ⟨RASAMAKHA⟩.

00:03:22.508 --> 00:03:25.545
mit vos hot geha- gearbet der tate?

00:03:25.545 --> 00:03:29.017
der tate, mit a, a katsev.

00:03:29.017 --> 00:03:31.772
s'iz geven a guter MATSAV in shtub?

00:03:31.772 --> 00:03:34.470
nit zeyer. nit keyn guter.

00:03:34.470 --> 00:03:37.903
vi iz geven der MATSAV HAKALKALI?

00:03:37.903 --> 00:03:41.903
koym koym oyf tsu ibertsulebn.

00:03:41.903 --> 00:03:42.356
mh.

00:03:42.356 --> 00:03:45.866
fun ale kleyne shtetlekh in Lite.

00:03:45.866 --> 00:03:48.715
vi hot oysgezen di shtetl?

00:03:48.715 --> 00:03:49.281
?

00:03:49.281 --> 00:03:51.771
vi hot oysgezen di shtetl?

00:03:51.771 --> 00:03:56.715
vi s'iz geven, vi, vi hot oysgezen.

00:03:56.715 --> 00:03:58.526
di mame

00:03:58.526 --> 00:04:02.299
der tate hot fardint a bisl.

00:04:02.299 --> 00:04:04.940
fun Amerike flegn mir krign

00:04:04.940 --> 00:04:06.582
ale yor

00:04:06.582 --> 00:04:08.865
tsu tsen doler

00:04:08.865 --> 00:04:12.091
oyf peysekh, oyf rosheshone.

00:04:12.091 --> 00:04:14.582
un ot azoy hot men gelebt.

00:04:14.582 --> 00:04:17.582
m'hot gehat eygene, eygenem gortn

00:04:17.582 --> 00:04:19.601
eygene bulves

00:04:19.601 --> 00:04:22.223
un keyn raykhkeyt iz nit geven

00:04:22.223 --> 00:04:24.771
un m'hot gelebt azoy.

00:04:24.771 --> 00:04:27.506
ale kinder hobn gelebt in eyn tsimer?

00:04:27.506 --> 00:04:29.430
ale kinder; s'iz geven

00:04:29.430 --> 00:04:33.355
dray tsimern, un ale kinder hobn mir gelebt in ale dray.

00:04:33.355 --> 00:04:35.316
a kleyn, a kleyn hoyz geven.

00:04:34.977 --> 00:04:39.770
a kleyne. m'iz geshlofn zalbe ⟨tsveyt⟩ in a bet.

00:04:39.770 --> 00:04:42.393
beyde brider hobn geshlofn tsuzamen.

00:04:42.393 --> 00:04:45.808
azoy me hot nit gekent hobn yeder kind zol hobn

00:04:45.808 --> 00:04:47.112
far zikh a tsimer.

00:04:47.112 --> 00:04:48.072
mh.

00:04:48.072 --> 00:04:51.242
a sakh yidn hobn gelebt dort in dem shtetl?

00:04:51.242 --> 00:04:57.052
dortn gemuzt zayn a draysik familyes in gantsn.

00:04:57.052 --> 00:05:00.335
s'iz geven gute YAKHASIM mit di goyim?

00:05:00.335 --> 00:05:02.826
ye, ye.

00:05:02.826 --> 00:05:07.298
in shtub iz geven a, di mishpokhe iz geven frum?

00:05:07.298 --> 00:05:09.147
zeyer un zeyer.

00:05:09.147 --> 00:05:10.694
dertseyl.

00:05:10.694 --> 00:05:11.581
mh?

00:05:11.581 --> 00:05:13.469
dertseyl vi s'iz geven.

00:05:12.920 --> 00:05:15.505
zey- zeyer frume.

00:05:15.505 --> 00:05:20.316
der tate dray mol in tog davnen, di mame a frume

00:05:20.316 --> 00:05:24.863
zeyer un zeyer DATI, zeyer un zeyer.

00:05:24.863 --> 00:05:27.467
der tate iz gegangen mit a bord?

00:05:27.467 --> 00:05:30.448
ye, mit a kleynem bord, ye.

00:05:30.448 --> 00:05:32.316
es iz geven a BET HAKNESET?

00:05:32.316 --> 00:05:35.146
ye, geven a BET HAKNESET.

00:05:35.146 --> 00:05:37.467
flegt davnen.

00:05:37.467 --> 00:05:40.203
di brider hobn gedavnt.

00:05:40.203 --> 00:05:44.184
flegt, ah, esn bentshn mit a mezumen.

00:05:44.184 --> 00:05:48.094
zeyer frum geven, zeyer, zeyer un zeyer frum.

00:05:49.617 --> 00:05:52.961
vos ge- vos gedenkst du fun di yontoyvim

00:05:52.961 --> 00:05:54.074
fun shtub?

00:05:54.074 --> 00:05:54.829
di y-

00:05:54.326 --> 00:05:55.470
vi iz geven, yo.

00:05:55.470 --> 00:05:59.150
oh, di yontoyvim iz geven zeyer freylekh.

00:05:59.150 --> 00:06:02.678
me flegt haltn fun yontev

00:06:02.678 --> 00:06:04.980
flegn kumen,

00:06:04.980 --> 00:06:10.111
ale kinder, di afile di khas- di shvester vos iz geven a khasene gehate

00:06:10.111 --> 00:06:12.489
un zi hot gelebt in Kovne

00:06:12.489 --> 00:06:16.526
flegt zi oyf peysekh oykh kumen bay di mamen.

00:06:16.526 --> 00:06:21.262
un me flegt, g- makhn a groysn seyder

00:06:21.262 --> 00:06:25.187
fraynt mit kosher mit

00:06:25.187 --> 00:06:31.526
mit, mit di hagode, azoy vi, azoy vi in hagode shteyt geshribn

00:06:31.526 --> 00:06:36.111
azoy flegt men makhn dem seyder.

00:06:39.224 --> 00:06:46.016
in velkhn, in velkhn yor bist du gegangen in di, in di kheyder?

00:06:46.016 --> 00:06:47.642
in kheyder?

00:06:47.153 --> 00:06:49.375
in dray yor oder mer?

00:06:49.375 --> 00:06:51.960
vi alt z- bist du geven?

00:06:51.960 --> 00:06:53.450
ikh gedenk nit.

00:06:54.167 --> 00:06:57.167
s'iz shoyn avek azoy fil yorn; ikh gedenk nit.

00:06:57.167 --> 00:06:59.431
vu host du gelernt?

00:06:59.431 --> 00:07:02.997
ersht azoy. s'iz geven a kleyne shtetl.

00:07:02.997 --> 00:07:05.506
me flegt haltn a lerer.

00:07:05.506 --> 00:07:08.789
ale f- flegn tsoln dem lerer gelt

00:07:08.789 --> 00:07:11.167
un mir hobn, un m'hot gelernt

00:07:11.167 --> 00:07:13.355
s'iz geven a BET KNESET

00:07:13.355 --> 00:07:15.431
an, a shul

00:07:15.431 --> 00:07:17.374
vos me flegt davnen.

00:07:17.374 --> 00:07:19.563
un dortn iz geven a vinkl

00:07:19.563 --> 00:07:24.299
vos flegt shteyn, azelkhene ⟨lafkes⟩ ⟨azane⟩ vos me

00:07:24.299 --> 00:07:26.940
tsu, tsu lernen far di kinder

00:07:26.940 --> 00:07:30.317
un dortn in a vinkl flegn mir lernen.

00:07:30.317 --> 00:07:32.979
meydlekh un yinglekh tsuzamen?

00:07:32.072 --> 00:07:35.223
meydlekh mit yinglekh tsuzamen, ye.

00:07:35.223 --> 00:07:36.864
oyf velkhe SAFA?

00:07:36.864 --> 00:07:38.306
oyf yidish ale?

00:07:37.883 --> 00:07:39.427
oyf ivrit. oyf ivrit.

00:07:39.336 --> 00:07:39.989
IVRIT.

00:07:39.732 --> 00:07:42.996
ober der ivrit iz geven nit azoy vi

00:07:42.996 --> 00:07:46.487
ersht in YISRAEL; der ivrit iz geven

00:07:46.487 --> 00:07:49.034
azoy vi shiler, me leyent.

00:07:49.034 --> 00:07:51.562
aza ivrit.

00:07:51.562 --> 00:07:53.826
un nokh dem letstn yor shoyn

00:07:53.826 --> 00:07:56.052
hot di mame mir avekgegebn

00:07:56.052 --> 00:07:59.524
in, in a BET seyfer shoyn

00:07:59.524 --> 00:08:03.330
a folksh- seyfer, nu, vi heyst dos oyf?

00:08:02.825 --> 00:08:03.447
AMAMI.

00:08:03.330 --> 00:08:04.882
AMAMI, ye.

00:08:04.882 --> 00:08:06.920
dortn hob ikh geendikt

00:08:06.920 --> 00:08:10.467
 dem BET seyfer. dortn merer nit geven

00:08:10.467 --> 00:08:12.581
keyn hekhere klasn tsum lernen.

00:08:12.581 --> 00:08:15.354
velkhn GIL hostu geendikt?

00:08:15.354 --> 00:08:16.958
ay, ikh gedenk nit.

00:08:16.958 --> 00:08:18.922
fertsn yor, fuftsn?

00:08:18.391 --> 00:08:21.637
UNK mistome bin ikh geven a fertsn yor,

00:08:21.637 --> 00:08:25.335
ikh gedenk nit genoy, um- umgefer.

00:08:25.335 --> 00:08:27.750
bist geven a gute TALMIDA?

00:08:27.750 --> 00:08:29.788
mh, mitl-mesik.

00:08:29.788 --> 00:08:31.599
host lib gehat tsu lernen?

00:08:31.599 --> 00:08:33.712
ye.

00:08:33.712 --> 00:08:37.326
vos hostu gemakht nokh di lern- n- nokh mitog?

00:08:36.108 --> 00:08:37.561
nokh di

00:08:37.561 --> 00:08:41.901
ikh hob geendikt le- geven, bin ikh geven in, in shtub bay di mame

00:08:41.901 --> 00:08:43.372
un az dernokh

00:08:43.372 --> 00:08:47.391
bin ikh gegangen zikh lernen far a shnayderke.

00:08:47.391 --> 00:08:49.043
in shtetl, yo?

00:08:48.391 --> 00:08:50.579
in shtetl, ye.

00:08:50.579 --> 00:08:53.259
bay, mm bay a daytshke.

00:08:53.259 --> 00:08:56.881
iz zi geven a daytshke, a shokhnte undzere di mame's.

00:08:56.881 --> 00:09:01.051
ober zi iz geven a lit- in Lite hot zi gelebt.

00:09:01.051 --> 00:09:04.881
un ikh hob zikh bay ir gelernt di shnayderay.

00:09:04.881 --> 00:09:07.674
un az di shvester hot khasene gehat

00:09:07.674 --> 00:09:09.730
ven zi hot gelebt in Kovne

00:09:09.730 --> 00:09:14.315
un der man iz ire geven a shnayder, hot geneyt mantlen.

00:09:14.315 --> 00:09:17.560
bin ikh avekgeforn bay di shvester

00:09:17.560 --> 00:09:18.899
un

00:09:18.899 --> 00:09:21.749
un ikh hob bay- geven bay ir

00:09:21.749 --> 00:09:27.956
un ikh hob geholfn neyen, nu, di, di shnayderay.

00:09:27.956 --> 00:09:30.088
vi hot geheysn di shvester?

00:09:30.088 --> 00:09:31.975
NEKHAMA.

00:09:31.975 --> 00:09:34.862
un, vi hot geheysn mitn man

00:09:34.862 --> 00:09:36.672
di nomen vos iz geven?

00:09:36.672 --> 00:09:39.295
dem man's? SAMUIL hot er geheysn.

00:09:39.220 --> 00:09:41.238
yo, ober der SHEM HAMISHPAKHA.

00:09:41.238 --> 00:09:42.993
LIfshits.

00:09:42.993 --> 00:09:45.625
un Nekhame hot gehat tsvey kinder, yo?

00:09:45.559 --> 00:09:48.201
tsvey kinder, a yingele un a meydele.

00:09:48.201 --> 00:09:49.974
gedenkst di nemen?

00:09:49.974 --> 00:09:52.578
ye, UNK gedenk

00:09:52.578 --> 00:09:56.069
di kinder oysgehode- gevo- oysgehodevet far mir.

00:09:56.069 --> 00:09:58.823
zey hobn mir azoy holt gehat di kinder

00:09:58.823 --> 00:10:04.924
az, ikh hob geveynt fun di kin- az di kinder iz,

00:10:04.924 --> 00:10:07.527
eyn- der yingele hot geheysn Nokhem

00:10:07.527 --> 00:10:11.904
un di meydele Libe. Libele. un der yingele Nokheml.

00:10:14.980 --> 00:10:19.980
 host gefilt, ANTISHEMIUT? s'iz geven ANTISHEMIUT

00:10:19.980 --> 00:10:20.904
in Kovne?

00:10:20.904 --> 00:10:25.376
far, neyn, far der milkhome, hot men zikh gornit gefilt azoy fil.

00:10:25.376 --> 00:10:28.055
s'iz geven a gut lebn, yo? a shtil.

00:10:28.055 --> 00:10:30.999
ye, a shtiler lebn. shtil, ruik.

00:10:30.999 --> 00:10:35.941
un dort in Kovne, vu, vu hot ir gevoynt tsuzamen.

00:10:35.941 --> 00:10:38.922
oyf LAISVES ALEJA, finf un draysik.

00:10:38.922 --> 00:10:43.243
dos iz di geven di glavne gas fun, fun Lite.

00:10:43.243 --> 00:10:49.564
Kovne iz geven di, di hoyptshtot fun Lite.

00:10:49.564 --> 00:10:51.847
mh.

00:10:51.847 --> 00:10:56.205
 ir hot gefilt, far di krig

00:10:56.205 --> 00:10:57.306
far di krig?

00:10:56.960 --> 00:10:57.507
ye.

00:10:57.507 --> 00:11:01.110
ir hot gefilt epes az s'gey- s- az s'vet zayn a krig?

00:11:01.110 --> 00:11:01.845
ye.

00:11:01.275 --> 00:11:02.677
m'hot geredt fun dem?

00:11:02.677 --> 00:11:05.507
ye. vi Hitler iz aroyf oyf der makht

00:11:05.507 --> 00:11:07.337
hot men shoyn geredt

00:11:07.337 --> 00:11:09.582
az s'vet nit zayn gut.

00:11:09.582 --> 00:11:14.110
ober der lebn iz gegangen; m'hot gelebt. m'hot gearbet.

00:11:14.110 --> 00:11:15.809
geven umetum

00:11:15.809 --> 00:11:19.884
kromen iz geven nor yidishe

00:11:19.884 --> 00:11:22.016
yidishe kromen.

00:11:22.016 --> 00:11:25.393
un, yidishe fabriklekh.

00:11:25.393 --> 00:11:30.129
m'hot gearbet, un un UNK der lebn iz gegangen normal.

00:11:30.129 --> 00:11:32.506
s'iz nisht geven keyn METAKH, gornisht.

00:11:32.506 --> 00:11:35.600
neyn. shtil geven, ruik.

00:11:35.600 --> 00:11:38.374
un, bist geforn aheym tsu di eltern oykh?

00:11:38.374 --> 00:11:41.299
ale, fleg forn azoy:

00:11:41.299 --> 00:11:44.770
oyf di yontoyvim fleg ikh forn

00:11:44.770 --> 00:11:46.582
un der nokh zumer

00:11:46.582 --> 00:11:49.525
flegt pasirn az s'flegt nit zayn keyn arbet.

00:11:49.525 --> 00:11:54.449
vayle s'iz mantlen, un zumer neyt men zikh nit keyn vinterdike mantlen.

00:11:54.449 --> 00:11:59.260
iz fleg ikh forn z- oyf zumer, fleg ikh ale mol tsuforn bay di mamen.

00:11:59.260 --> 00:12:05.505
zayn a monat tsayt, a genoye monat, un nakher forn tsurik.

00:12:05.505 --> 00:12:10.411
un az du host gelebt in Kovne, iz du host geshribn briv?

00:12:10.411 --> 00:12:12.755
m'hot gekent shraybn briv, yo?

00:12:12.053 --> 00:12:14.524
ye, ye, far vos nit?

00:12:14.524 --> 00:12:18.505
brivn d- ershtns flegn kumen zeyer oft fun shtub

00:12:18.505 --> 00:12:21.052
 bay di shvester

00:12:21.052 --> 00:12:27.410
un do flegt kumen der bruder, do flegt kumen di shvester, do flegt kumen tsu forn di mame, un a mol der tate

00:12:27.410 --> 00:12:30.844
un geven zeyer a, mh

00:12:30.844 --> 00:12:35.260
nit geven opgezundert.

00:12:35.260 --> 00:12:37.429
m'hot geredt fun Erets Yisroel?

00:12:37.429 --> 00:12:39.580
nor fun Erets Yisroel.

00:12:39.580 --> 00:12:42.203
vos gedenkstu? bist geven a TSIONIT?

00:12:42.203 --> 00:12:43.882
ye, ye.

00:12:43.882 --> 00:12:44.908
bist gegangen in a

00:12:44.241 --> 00:12:45.014
un nokh

00:12:44.979 --> 00:12:45.953
TNUAT NOAR?

00:12:45.953 --> 00:12:47.765
ye, ge- s'iz geven

00:12:47.765 --> 00:12:49.787
bay undz in Kovne iz geven

00:12:49.787 --> 00:12:52.655
nu, klubn. a klub.

00:12:52.655 --> 00:12:53.723
MOADON.

00:12:53.636 --> 00:12:54.693
MOADON, ye.

00:12:54.693 --> 00:12:59.146
vos me flegt nor vegn Erets Yisroel, flegn tantsn a hoyra

00:12:59.146 --> 00:13:02.768
un flegt nor UNK, ober vos, un flegt geyn oyf HAKHSHARA

00:13:02.768 --> 00:13:05.089
ot o mayn man iz geven oyf HAKHSHARA

00:13:05.089 --> 00:13:10.165
nor vos, me flegt nit krigen keyn sertifikatn; s'iz nit geven.

00:13:10.165 --> 00:13:16.428
vos, ven me volt ge- arayngelozn dan in, in ISRA-, in, in Erets Yisroel

00:13:16.428 --> 00:13:21.013
voltn ongekumen a groyse yugnt volt gekumen fun Lite.

00:13:21.013 --> 00:13:27.862
nor, m'hot nit gekent forn; m'hot nit gelozn forn.

00:13:27.862 --> 00:13:29.881
s'iz geven zeyer a sakh.

00:13:29.881 --> 00:13:32.692
der gantser yugnt hot nor ge- nor

00:13:32.692 --> 00:13:35.447
tsu forn oyf Erets Yisroel.

00:13:35.447 --> 00:13:39.427
oyber s'iz ver vu nit a mol ver nit iz avekgeforn

00:13:39.427 --> 00:13:44.465
flegt men tantsn un zingen un

00:13:44.465 --> 00:13:47.773
un lider zingen alerley nor oyf Erets Y-

00:13:47.201 --> 00:13:49.333
gedenkst epes a lid?

00:13:49.333 --> 00:13:52.258
UNK nit gedenken.

00:13:52.258 --> 00:13:53.805
dos gedenkstu?

00:13:53.805 --> 00:14:01.144
huh flegt forn epes, gedenk

00:14:01.144 --> 00:14:02.182
vos ge- v-

00:14:02.182 --> 00:14:05.432
vi iz geven az di milkhome hot, ongehoybn?

00:14:05.432 --> 00:14:09.073
oh, di milkhome, dos iz geven a shrek.

00:14:09.073 --> 00:14:11.413
di zelbe litviner

00:14:11.413 --> 00:14:15.734
vos zey hobn gelebt azoy gut mit di yidn, afile in di shtetlekh

00:14:15.734 --> 00:14:21.243
zaynen gevorn ROTSKHIM.

00:14:21.243 --> 00:14:24.243
glaykh zuntik

00:14:24.243 --> 00:14:28.507
hobn di daytshn bombardirt

00:14:28.507 --> 00:14:32.092
kovner erodrom.

00:14:32.092 --> 00:14:34.073
in velkhn TARICH iz dos geven?

00:14:34.073 --> 00:14:39.054
dos iz geven dem eyn un tsvantsikstn yuni, eyn in fertsikstn yor.

00:14:39.054 --> 00:14:45.186
biz eyn un fertsikstn yor, ir hot gehert vos tut zikh in Poyln, un in in Daytshland?

00:14:43.658 --> 00:14:45.997
ye, ye. gehert.

00:14:45.997 --> 00:14:50.544
gehert, flegt shraybn in di tsaytungen; m'hot alts gehert. ober

00:14:50.544 --> 00:14:53.394
s'flegn onkumen poylishe yidn

00:14:53.394 --> 00:14:55.997
in, in Kovne

00:14:55.997 --> 00:14:58.110
antlofene fun Poyln

00:14:58.110 --> 00:15:01.393
ober vos m'hot dokh keyner keyn zakh nit gekent helfn.

00:15:01.393 --> 00:15:06.355
der lebn iz zikh gegangen normal; m'hot gearbet un

00:15:06.355 --> 00:15:11.672
un azoy iz gegangen, geven, der lebn vi geherik iz.

00:15:11.672 --> 00:15:12.223
mh.

00:15:12.223 --> 00:15:14.591
un ven s'hot oysgebrokhn di milkhome

00:15:13.846 --> 00:15:15.374
yo, dertseyl, yo.

00:15:16.770 --> 00:15:18.255
hobn zey bom-

00:15:17.544 --> 00:15:18.827
in a zuntik, yo?

00:15:18.827 --> 00:15:21.544
a zuntikdiker tog iz dos geven.

00:15:21.544 --> 00:15:23.582
fir a zeyger in der fri

00:15:23.582 --> 00:15:25.242
hobn zey bombardirt

00:15:25.242 --> 00:15:28.128
dem erodrom.

00:15:28.128 --> 00:15:30.600
un zuntik

00:15:30.600 --> 00:15:36.053
un montik hobn shoyn di litviner gemakht pogromen.

00:15:36.053 --> 00:15:38.864
zaynen avek sh- Kovne

00:15:38.864 --> 00:15:42.034
iz geven a forshtot, Slabodke.

00:15:42.034 --> 00:15:45.581
der ershter pogrom iz geven in Slabodke.

00:15:45.581 --> 00:15:49.222
zaynen arayn in di shtiber, un zey hobn oysgeharget

00:15:49.222 --> 00:15:50.619
un baroybt

00:15:50.619 --> 00:15:52.203
ale zakhn

00:15:52.203 --> 00:15:58.184
un, un, un geharget mentshn.

00:15:58.184 --> 00:15:59.731
vayter, yo?

00:15:59.731 --> 00:16:03.448
di litviner hobn genug fargosn yidishe blut.

00:16:03.448 --> 00:16:06.373
glaykh zaynen zey gegangen mit biksn

00:16:06.373 --> 00:16:08.184
in di hent

00:16:08.184 --> 00:16:10.316
oyf di gasn

00:16:10.316 --> 00:16:16.354
un der yid in a por teg arum hot men shoyn nit getort geyn afile oyfn trotuar.

00:16:16.354 --> 00:16:22.108
m'hot gedarft geyn oyfn KVISH, oyfn gas.

00:16:22.108 --> 00:16:24.391
un

00:16:24.391 --> 00:16:29.976
un m'hot moyre gehat, yeder eyner in di hayzer hot moyre gehat; me flegt zikh farmakhn.

00:16:29.976 --> 00:16:32.353
far vos vayl es flegn arayngeyn

00:16:32.353 --> 00:16:35.731
in di hayzer hargenen un, un un

00:16:35.731 --> 00:16:38.731
un rabeven.

00:16:38.731 --> 00:16:41.372
di litviner.

00:16:41.372 --> 00:16:45.692
vos iz gevorn, vos iz geven bay aykh in shtub?

00:16:45.692 --> 00:16:48.636
ikh bin geven bay di shvester.

00:16:48.636 --> 00:16:53.466
host gevust vos tut zikh bay di mishpokhe, bay di eltern, bay di brider?

00:16:53.466 --> 00:16:57.239
fun onfang hot men nit gevust.

00:16:57.239 --> 00:17:00.013
m'hot fun onfang m'hot alts gemeynt az

00:17:00.013 --> 00:17:03.107
men, men, in a shtetl

00:17:03.107 --> 00:17:07.560
mir, mayn shvo- mayn bruder un di shvegerin

00:17:07.560 --> 00:17:09.711
iz grade geven in Kovne

00:17:09.711 --> 00:17:11.692
hot gezogt di shvegerin

00:17:11.692 --> 00:17:13.805
"kumt, ir veyst vos?" zogt zi.

00:17:13.805 --> 00:17:16.126
"a poyer darf kumen mit a fur;

00:17:16.126 --> 00:17:19.050
lomir ale avekforn in Kruki.

00:17:19.050 --> 00:17:25.107
ikh hob" zogt zi "mel, un ikh hob nokh alts, es vet nokh klekn," zogt zi "vi lang vet doyern di milkhome.

00:17:25.107 --> 00:17:27.541
mir veln ir ariberlebn.

00:17:27.541 --> 00:17:29.182
kumt bay undz."

00:17:29.182 --> 00:17:31.145
keyner hot zikh nit forgeshtelt

00:17:31.145 --> 00:17:33.239
oyf aza bitere milkhome

00:17:33.239 --> 00:17:37.735
az di litviner veln azoy vern ibergekerte.

00:17:37.735 --> 00:17:40.885
m'hot gelebt in di shtetlekh gut mit di litviner

00:17:40.885 --> 00:17:44.527
un di zelbe litviner vos zey hobn gelebt gut mit di yidn

00:17:44.527 --> 00:17:47.659
zaynen gevorn ot dernokh rotskhim.

00:17:47.659 --> 00:17:50.527
vos hot ir gemakht, ir hot geforn keyn Kruki?

00:17:50.527 --> 00:17:53.980
neyn. mir zaynen nit geforn.

00:17:53.980 --> 00:17:57.753
eyn mol bin ikh gegangen mitn bruder.

00:17:57.753 --> 00:17:59.395
vi hot er geheysn?

00:17:59.395 --> 00:18:02.489
Yosef.

00:18:02.489 --> 00:18:07.753
mitn bruder zaynen mir gegangen, un mir zayn- dos iz geven

00:18:07.753 --> 00:18:13.130
zuntik, montik, kh'hob gezogt az dos hot gemuzt zayn a dinstik.

00:18:13.130 --> 00:18:15.319
zaynen mir gegangen

00:18:15.319 --> 00:18:18.300
mitn bruder a kuk ton vos tut zikh

00:18:18.300 --> 00:18:22.243
bay dem, bay dem bruder vos er darf avekforn, barn eltern.

00:18:22.243 --> 00:18:23.828
vi hot geheysn der eltern?

00:18:23.828 --> 00:18:24.904
Moyshe.

00:18:24.904 --> 00:18:28.507
ye, un di shv- di shvegerin geheysn Libe.

00:18:28.507 --> 00:18:30.336
zaynen mir gegangen

00:18:29.715 --> 00:18:30.507
in Kovne?

00:18:30.507 --> 00:18:31.865
in Kovne.

00:18:31.865 --> 00:18:34.563
ober zey hobn gelebt in Kruki.

00:18:34.563 --> 00:18:36.846
nor er iz dan geven krank

00:18:36.846 --> 00:18:40.016
der bruder, iz er geven in BET KHOLIM.

00:18:40.016 --> 00:18:41.545
un fun BET KHOLIM

00:18:41.545 --> 00:18:44.922
un zey, zi hot dortn gehat fraynt eygene.

00:18:44.922 --> 00:18:47.545
iz, ah, iz zi geven bay di fraynt

00:18:47.545 --> 00:18:49.677
un az er iz geven in BET KHOLIM

00:18:49.677 --> 00:18:51.243
hot men im gezogt

00:18:51.243 --> 00:18:54.696
"nem a shtekn

00:18:54.696 --> 00:18:58.283
un gey aroys vayl in BET KHOLIM iz nit gut.

00:18:58.283 --> 00:19:00.566
gey aroys fun BET KHOLIM."

00:19:00.566 --> 00:19:03.546
hot er azoy geton, ot, mit a shtekn

00:19:03.546 --> 00:19:04.923
un er iz gekumen

00:19:04.923 --> 00:19:08.150
tsu di froy in dortn bay ire fraynt.

00:19:08.150 --> 00:19:11.848
un zi dan, mir zaynen eyn mol geven mit di shvester

00:19:11.848 --> 00:19:14.376
hot zi gezogt "lomir forn in Kruki

00:19:14.376 --> 00:19:18.188
Kruki iz ruik shtil, ale eygene poyerim

00:19:18.188 --> 00:19:20.169
zey ver vet undz tshepenen.

00:19:20.169 --> 00:19:22.471
mir veln di milkhome ariberlebn."

00:19:22.471 --> 00:19:25.603
zaynen ikh mitn bruder zaynen mir gegangen a kuk ton

00:19:25.603 --> 00:19:26.905
vos tut zikh

00:19:26.905 --> 00:19:29.319
bay dem ts- bay dem eltern bruder.

00:19:29.319 --> 00:19:31.413
geyendik oyfn gas

00:19:31.413 --> 00:19:36.640
hobn mir, oyfn trotuar hot men shoyn nit getort geyn; mir zaynen gegangen oyfn

00:19:36.640 --> 00:19:37.928
nu, oyfn shos-

00:19:37.408 --> 00:19:38.438
oyfn KVISH.

00:19:38.338 --> 00:19:39.489
oyfn KVISH.

00:19:39.489 --> 00:19:42.368
un ir hot gehat, gele mogn-doved?

00:19:42.281 --> 00:19:43.264
neyn, nokh nit.

00:19:43.187 --> 00:19:43.969
nokh nit.

00:19:43.470 --> 00:19:46.432
di gele mogn-doved hot men gemakht in geto.

00:19:46.432 --> 00:19:48.640
geyendik azoy

00:19:48.640 --> 00:19:50.791
mayn bruder hot gearbet

00:19:50.791 --> 00:19:53.828
in a, in a MAKOLET.

00:19:53.828 --> 00:19:55.337
ye.

00:19:55.337 --> 00:19:58.884
un dortn bay shosay iz geven a MAKOLET

00:19:58.884 --> 00:20:03.130
iz arayn a sheygetsl, un er iz gegangen ganvenen tsukerkes.

00:20:03.130 --> 00:20:07.526
hot der bruder geshrien oyf im, hot er onghoybn veynen un antlofn.

00:20:07.526 --> 00:20:09.752
iz geyendik azoy glaykh

00:20:09.752 --> 00:20:13.318
geyt tsu a po- un di-o, di litviner

00:20:13.318 --> 00:20:15.564
zaynen shoyn gegangen mit di biksn

00:20:15.564 --> 00:20:20.092
oysgeshtelte, un zey zaynen shoyn gegangen oyf di gasn hot men gegangen.

00:20:20.092 --> 00:20:25.752
geyt tsu di poyerte, makht zi azoy tsu dem, ot der vos er geyt mitn biks

00:20:25.752 --> 00:20:27.789
zogt zi oyf litvish:

00:20:27.789 --> 00:20:32.016
"nem im tsu," zogt zi. "er hot geshlogn mayn kind."

00:20:32.016 --> 00:20:36.337
zogt er, mayn bruder "ikh hob dem kind nit gesglogn.

00:20:36.337 --> 00:20:41.525
er iz gegangen ganvenen di tsukerkes, hob ikh geshrien oyf im, hot er zikhkh geveynt."

00:20:41.525 --> 00:20:43.582
un zi, "neyn!

00:20:43.582 --> 00:20:47.562
er er hot im geshlogn. nem im, nem im!"

00:20:47.562 --> 00:20:50.883
i- zogt er, der mitn biks

00:20:50.883 --> 00:20:52.355
"kum."

00:20:52.355 --> 00:20:55.525
zogt mayn bruder "mayn shvester veys keyn zakh nit.

00:20:55.525 --> 00:20:57.261
UNK

00:20:57.261 --> 00:20:58.977
dos iz mayn shvester."

00:20:58.977 --> 00:21:01.374
zogt der goy, "UNK PAIMK

00:21:01.374 --> 00:21:03.544
nem im oykh, nem."

00:21:03.544 --> 00:21:06.732
beydn ho-, er firt undz

00:21:06.732 --> 00:21:10.996
arayngefirt dortn vu di politsey iz geven

00:21:10.996 --> 00:21:15.562
un zitsn shoyn a sakh mener un froyen.

00:21:15.562 --> 00:21:22.033
der iz far dos shuldik, dos zenen glaykh in di ershte teg fun vi s'iz oysgebrokhn di milkhome.

00:21:22.033 --> 00:21:26.958
un m'hot undz arayngefirt bay eynem, o- shraybt a protokol.

00:21:26.958 --> 00:21:28.920
shraybt un shraybt, zogt er,

00:21:28.920 --> 00:21:32.467
"⟨MES NE PADARYSIME KE, KE RUSAI PADARE⟩."

00:21:32.467 --> 00:21:34.109
heyst dos oyf yidish iz

00:21:34.109 --> 00:21:38.486
mi- az "mir veln nit makhn vi di rusn hobn gemakht," ye.

00:21:38.486 --> 00:21:44.731
der end iz geven az beshas der bruder hot gearbet in dem, in di krom

00:21:44.731 --> 00:21:47.014
iz dortn flegt arayngeyn

00:21:47.014 --> 00:21:51.089
eyner a daytsh, nor a litvinisher daytsh

00:21:51.089 --> 00:21:53.448
un er hot zeyer gut mit im gelebt.

00:21:53.448 --> 00:21:56.089
un er iz shoyn gevorn oykhet

00:21:56.089 --> 00:22:00.184
geholfn tsu di daytshn, un er hot im gezen

00:22:00.184 --> 00:22:02.184
az m'hot undz tsugenumen

00:22:02.184 --> 00:22:04.825
un mayn bruder hot zikh UNK mit im.

00:22:04.825 --> 00:22:09.636
iz kentik az er hot geheysn undz aroys- az me zol undz aroyslozn.

00:22:09.636 --> 00:22:12.862
z- dortn zaynen mir opgeven a tsayt, a tsayt

00:22:12.862 --> 00:22:15.278
biz nokh arum mitog tsayt

00:22:15.278 --> 00:22:16.995
un

00:22:16.995 --> 00:22:18.711
m'hot undz aroysgelozn.

00:22:18.711 --> 00:22:21.938
m'hot undz zaynen mir shoyn baym bruder nit gegangen

00:22:21.938 --> 00:22:26.240
nor mir zaynen shoyn gelofn tsurik tsu di shvester, bay di shvester.

00:22:26.240 --> 00:22:30.423
bay di shvester shoyn nit gevust vos ibertsutrakhtn un vu zaynen mir ahingekumen.

00:22:30.423 --> 00:22:31.642
bay Nekhame, yo?

00:22:31.183 --> 00:22:32.617
bay Nekhamen, ye.

00:22:32.617 --> 00:22:34.409
az gekumen bay Nekhamen

00:22:34.409 --> 00:22:36.918
nu, me hot dos hot zikh farendikt.

00:22:36.918 --> 00:22:42.503
un zey, mayn bruder mit di shvegerin, zaynen avekgeforn in Kruki.

00:22:42.503 --> 00:22:44.956
yo. vos iz geven vayter?

00:22:44.956 --> 00:22:48.333
in Kruki iz geven

00:22:48.333 --> 00:22:54.447
di litviner, di ale litviner vos hobn gelebt azoy gut mit di yidn

00:22:54.447 --> 00:22:56.107
un zey flegn zogn

00:22:56.107 --> 00:23:00.031
az du bist mayn bruder, ye? ⟨TU MANO BROLIS⟩, ye?

00:23:00.031 --> 00:23:01.333
UNK

00:23:01.333 --> 00:23:06.729
un m'hot gelebt gut, zaynen zey gevorn az dernokh rotskhim.

00:23:06.729 --> 00:23:11.748
di nit ot azoy fil di daytshn vi di litviner hobn merer

00:23:11.748 --> 00:23:13.974
fargosn yidishe blut.

00:23:13.974 --> 00:23:18.314
zey hobn glaykh genumen in a por teg arum, un ikh veys nit vifl epes

00:23:18.314 --> 00:23:22.257
mh merer, efsher in vo- in vokhn arum

00:23:22.257 --> 00:23:25.207
genoy veys ikh nit velkhe tsayt

00:23:25.207 --> 00:23:26.716
hot men genumen

00:23:26.716 --> 00:23:30.093
di g- un in shtub iz shoyn geblibn azoy

00:23:30.093 --> 00:23:32.904
in gantsn: di mame un der tate

00:23:32.904 --> 00:23:36.300
un di shvester Khaye, ye.

00:23:36.300 --> 00:23:39.772
der bruder iz geven a khasene gehater in Kruki.

00:23:39.772 --> 00:23:40.829
vi hot er geheysn?

00:23:40.829 --> 00:23:42.734
Moyshe, der elterer.

00:23:42.734 --> 00:23:44.432
der tsveyter bruder

00:23:44.432 --> 00:23:46.328
vos iz geven khasene gehat

00:23:45.734 --> 00:23:46.791
Yosef.

00:23:46.791 --> 00:23:47.470
Berl.

00:23:47.470 --> 00:23:48.724
ah, Berl, yo.

00:23:48.187 --> 00:23:50.187
Berl. hot er gelebt

00:23:50.187 --> 00:23:52.074
nit vayt fun Yurbrik.

00:23:52.074 --> 00:23:53.715
a sh- oykh a shtetl

00:23:53.715 --> 00:23:56.752
lebn, in Lite.

00:23:56.752 --> 00:23:57.696
dos iz oykh

00:23:57.696 --> 00:24:03.545
nit vayt arum Nemen, in Lite geven a taykh, a Nemen hot er geheysn.

00:24:03.545 --> 00:24:08.866
er hot dortn gelebt; er hot gehat a froy un er hot shoyn gehat a yingele a faynem.

00:24:08.866 --> 00:24:11.885
ah, iz,

00:24:11.885 --> 00:24:17.809
 ye, ⟨vos hob ikh gevelt zogn?⟩ ye,ho- hobn zey genum-, azoy, iz dokh geven in shtub iz geblibn nor

00:24:17.809 --> 00:24:19.621
di mame un der tate

00:24:19.621 --> 00:24:22.470
un di shvester, di Khaye

00:24:22.470 --> 00:24:24.149
un der bruder

00:24:24.149 --> 00:24:27.791
ho- hot gelebt mit di froy, bazunder.

00:24:27.791 --> 00:24:31.583
do hot men genumen mener oyf der arbet.

00:24:31.583 --> 00:24:35.508
mener hot men genumen oyf der arbet, un m'hot genumen mayn bruder.

00:24:35.508 --> 00:24:41.093
un mayn shvester, az zi hot gekent ale poyerim dortn UNK az me ken zikh eyner dem tsveytn.

00:24:41.093 --> 00:24:43.394
zogt zi tsum poyer

00:24:43.394 --> 00:24:49.735
zogt zi "vos nemstu im? du zest dokh az er ge-, er iz kra- er hinkt un er geyt mit a shtekn. nem im nit."

00:24:49.735 --> 00:24:52.074
az er git ir a shlep

00:24:52.074 --> 00:24:53.564
zogt er azoy:

00:24:53.564 --> 00:24:56.508
"oyber du, er ken nit geyn, iz kum.

00:24:56.508 --> 00:24:58.451
vestu im hitn."

00:24:58.451 --> 00:25:01.753
un er hot ir shoyn nit opgelozn.

00:25:01.753 --> 00:25:04.772
iz zi avek di shvester mit di mener

00:25:04.772 --> 00:25:07.904
geblibn iz mayn mame eyner aleyn.

00:25:07.904 --> 00:25:11.621
mayn mame iz geven letstns zeyer a kranke froy.

00:25:11.621 --> 00:25:14.489
a shvakhe un a kranke.

00:25:14.489 --> 00:25:16.942
flegt zi loyfn bay di shvegerin

00:25:16.942 --> 00:25:19.413
bay di shnur UNK kumen di mame's

00:25:19.413 --> 00:25:22.413
bay Libe'n, flegt zi dortn zayn.

00:25:22.413 --> 00:25:24.300
un eyner aleyn.

00:25:24.300 --> 00:25:26.153
un der tate vos iz geven?

00:25:25.658 --> 00:25:29.696
der tate iz avek m- oyf der arbet, hot men genumen ale mener.

00:25:29.696 --> 00:25:32.828
iz der tate avek un der bruder avek

00:25:32.828 --> 00:25:36.790
un m'hot tsugenumen di shvester, ye.

00:25:36.790 --> 00:25:39.469
zey avekgefirt oyf der arbet

00:25:39.469 --> 00:25:41.620
un di mame iz gegangen tsu di shnurn.

00:25:41.620 --> 00:25:45.695
un di mame flegt geyn tsu di sh- a gantsn tog flegt zi zayn tsu di shnur

00:25:45.695 --> 00:25:48.903
un bay nakht flegt zi kumen in shtub shlofn.

00:25:48.903 --> 00:25:51.846
PITOM hot men UNK genumen

00:25:51.846 --> 00:25:53.884
di vayber oykh.

00:25:53.884 --> 00:25:56.601
hot men tsuzamengenumen ale froyen

00:25:56.601 --> 00:26:01.412
vayl s'iz geblibn nor di froyen; di mener hot men frier tsuzamengenumen.

00:26:01.412 --> 00:26:04.865
hot men genumen di froyen; azoy di mener

00:26:04.865 --> 00:26:09.205
hot men tsuzamengenumen. m'hot zey gefirt a por teg oyf der arbet

00:26:09.205 --> 00:26:13.449
un ⟨m'hot zey⟩ avekgefirt, un dort iz geven a shtetl Sharki.

00:26:13.449 --> 00:26:16.770
oykh in Lite; dos iz geven nit vayt fun Kruki.

00:26:16.770 --> 00:26:23.355
m'hot zey dortn avekgefirt, un m'hot zey alemen dortn oysgeshosn.

00:26:23.355 --> 00:26:27.883
di sh- di glavne shisers zaynen geven di litviner.

00:26:27.883 --> 00:26:30.732
zey zaynen geven di glavne shisers.

00:26:30.732 --> 00:26:32.770
der daytsh hot geheysn

00:26:32.770 --> 00:26:35.996
un zey zaynen geven di glavne shisers.

00:26:35.996 --> 00:26:38.260
un di b- un di mamen

00:26:38.260 --> 00:26:40.335
mit di ale froyen

00:26:40.335 --> 00:26:44.958
iz in a bisl tsayt arum, ikh veys nit tsi oyf vifl vokhn, tsi vos

00:26:44.958 --> 00:26:48.071
hot men tsuzamgenumen ale froyen.

00:26:48.071 --> 00:26:51.958
m'hot avekgefirt, iz geven nokh a shtetl, Sapizhishok.

00:26:51.958 --> 00:26:55.109
dos iz geven nenter tsu Kovne. shoyn.

00:26:55.109 --> 00:26:57.920
un m'hot zey dortn alemen

00:26:57.920 --> 00:27:01.071
umgebrakht, ye.

00:27:01.071 --> 00:27:04.052
ot vel ikh dertseyln fun a litvin:

00:27:04.052 --> 00:27:05.052
dos iz UNK

00:27:04.510 --> 00:27:07.882
dos iz ge- SLIKHA, dos iz geven in eyn un fertsikster yor?

00:27:07.882 --> 00:27:10.033
in eyn un fertsikstn yor.

00:27:10.033 --> 00:27:10.877
vayter.

00:27:10.429 --> 00:27:11.867
vi di milkhome iz oysgebrokhn.

00:27:12.165 --> 00:27:14.750
dem alts in dem yor.

00:27:14.750 --> 00:27:15.920
az s'hot oys-

00:27:15.920 --> 00:27:20.448
vi s'hot oysge⟨brokhn⟩ iz di ershte teg hot men nit gekent aroysgeyn.

00:27:20.448 --> 00:27:22.165
ye.

00:27:22.165 --> 00:27:25.674
vu di, un di di shvester

00:27:25.674 --> 00:27:27.825
iz dokh geven mit tsvey kinder

00:27:27.825 --> 00:27:30.127
iz an UNK me darf dokh esn

00:27:30.127 --> 00:27:31.816
shoyn nito vos tsum esn

00:27:31.315 --> 00:27:33.259
yetst dertseylstu fun Kovne, yo?

00:27:33.259 --> 00:27:35.372
dos iz fun Kovne, in Kovne geven, ye.

00:27:35.372 --> 00:27:37.315
vi s'hot oysgebrokhn in Kovne di krig

00:27:37.315 --> 00:27:42.334
er, az du bist geven in Kovne mit di shvester, ir hot gevust vos tut zikh in Kruki?

00:27:42.334 --> 00:27:44.108
az m'hot avekgenumen ale

00:27:44.108 --> 00:27:44.881
neyn,

00:27:44.881 --> 00:27:46.091
mir hobn mit gevust.

00:27:45.257 --> 00:27:46.642
biz shpeter es iz

00:27:46.224 --> 00:27:48.749
nor ven, ven hob ikh zikh dervust

00:27:48.749 --> 00:27:52.995
vayl eyne iz gekumen, dos iz geven az mir zaynen geven in geto

00:27:52.995 --> 00:27:56.296
az mir zaynen geven in geto iz gekumen eyne

00:27:56.296 --> 00:27:58.484
di mame's a shokhnte

00:27:58.484 --> 00:28:01.824
un zi hot oyfgezukht undz in geto

00:28:01.824 --> 00:28:03.598
un zi iz geven bay undz

00:28:03.598 --> 00:28:06.673
un zi hot dos undz alts dertseylt.

00:28:06.673 --> 00:28:08.654
ye. nokh

00:28:08.654 --> 00:28:11.900
nu, do, glaykh vi s'hot oysgebrokhn di milkhome

00:28:11.900 --> 00:28:14.975
dos iz geven in Kovne, iz

00:28:14.975 --> 00:28:19.107
hot shoyn, me darf zikh, hobn vos tsum, iz es, hot men gezogt

00:28:19.107 --> 00:28:22.339
az vu mayn shvester hot gelebt az antkegn

00:28:22.339 --> 00:28:24.735
ibern veg, iz geven

00:28:24.735 --> 00:28:28.301
ahm, ah, a krom fun

00:28:28.301 --> 00:28:30.640
broyt, khale

00:28:30.640 --> 00:28:32.395
fun di zakhn.

00:28:32.395 --> 00:28:35.112
az m'git a khale

00:28:35.112 --> 00:28:38.527
g- az me shteyt in, in ⟨TOR⟩, in otshered

00:28:38.527 --> 00:28:40.565
un, in rey heyst es,

00:28:40.565 --> 00:28:43.414
git men yedn eynem a khale.

00:28:43.414 --> 00:28:47.282
bin ikh avekgegangen, un ikh hob zikh oykh geshtelt in rey

00:28:47.282 --> 00:28:49.320
ikh hob zikh azoy tsuzamengedreyt

00:28:49.320 --> 00:28:51.942
un di tsure tsum vant az me zol mir nit

00:28:51.942 --> 00:28:54.885
me zol nit zen az ikh bin a yidishe

00:28:54.885 --> 00:28:56.583
un

00:28:56.583 --> 00:28:59.262
un do, ge- shteyendik azoy

00:28:59.262 --> 00:29:00.753
her ikh

00:29:00.753 --> 00:29:04.017
az s'kumt, geyt tsu a a litovets

00:29:04.017 --> 00:29:06.583
far mayne oygn shteyt er mir nokh ersht

00:29:06.583 --> 00:29:08.055
a hoykher

00:29:08.055 --> 00:29:11.527
mit a biks in hant; makht er azoy:

00:29:11.527 --> 00:29:14.998
"ikh," zogt er, "hob nekhtn" zogt er, "oysgeshosn

00:29:14.998 --> 00:29:16.564
SIMTU ZYDU"

00:29:16.564 --> 00:29:21.830
hundert yidn hot er oysgeshosn in Aleksot. ye.
